  "synopsis": "In reality, all extreme dreams contain terrifying energy. Only by sending these dreams to another dimension—the Dream Realm—can this energy be prevented from distorting and disrupting the real world. The unconventional Ren Xiaochong is chosen by a Dream Ferryman from the Dream Realm by chance to become a Dream Warrior of the Flute-Seeing Tower, embarking on a strange dream-transforming journey. While his conflict with his companion Wu Jia intensifies, another tower, the Ink-Decision Tower, secretly plots an invasion of the Flute-Seeing Tower, uncovering a long-dormant secret legend of the Dream Realm…\n\n(Source: Douban, translated)",
